        "TileImage": "$($repository 54207b47-c289-49a0-944f-b52201baa429).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47.\r\rYour target is Olive Haskel, a resident of Whittleton Creek. Haskel spends his days since retirement sitting on his porch, sipping lemonade and feuding with local children. Recently, he seems to have turned a new leaf to the youths, offering them drinks. However, our client, a member of the community, has learned a dark secret.\r\rHaskel has spiked his lemonade on several occasions, poisoning children in a petty display of spite.\r\rThe client wants an &quot;accidental&quot; death, 47.",
